job-step.description: Topic Inbound consumes tuples from a specified topic in the DPC and emits them to be processed by downstream job steps.

JSON Normalization takes a single JSON object that was received as a string value and extracts various values. For each extracted value, it then adds a field to the tuple emitted to the output stream.
Formatter uses a FreeMarker template to build a single string from the input tuple values, and sends the converted string to a downstream job step.
Topic Outbound receives input fields from the previous job step, and then generates tuples and sends them to the topic associated with the job step.
